<br>
Chain + Evade1 &lt; Evade3 + reinforced. The damage we get isn't lessened by all that much, and not getting hit defeats getting hit. Even plate users fall fast, and complain that chain+evade 1 is actually better than plate.<br>
<br>
Damage-wise, we don't do anymore damage than a blademaster (IMO). We're actually behind because of DT not being useable and TW add damage and prevents crits.<br>
<br>
Because of the recent changes, i'd say the merc falls short of the BM. Not by much, but noticeably so. A bezerker still hands me my soiled shorts, not nearly as much as befor, but he's still a threat (more so that I am to him, in my case).<br>
<br>
